Interface AssetExportService

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface AssetExportService
    AssetExportService provides capabilities to export / import Correspondence Management Assets as CRX packages.

      • getImportInfo2

        @Deprecated
Map<String,Object> getImportInfo2(Downloadable file)
                                       throws ICCException
        Deprecated. 
        List all the assets, categories and data dictionary to be imported from the file.
        Parameters:
        file - Downloadable object having zip file content
        Returns:
        map containing following key value pairs:
        Key Value
        CRXPackageNames (List<String>) Names of CRX packages being imported. CM package will contain multiple CRX packages.
        PackageFileName (String) Name of the package file.
        NewAssets (List<Object>) List of assets being imported first time on the system.
        OldAssets (List<Object>) List of assets being imported which already exist on the system.
        Throws:
        ICCException
        Since:
        10.0.5

      • importAsset3

        @Deprecated
List<String> importAsset3(String importInfoNodePath)
                               throws ICCException
        Deprecated. 
        Imports Asset with the info stored at node specified by node path passed input. The node in repo should contain the following info
        Key Value
        CRXPackageNames (List<String>) Names of CRX packages being imported. CM package will contain multiple CRX packages.
        PackageFileName (String) Name of the package file.
        NewAssets (List<Object>) List of assets being imported first time on the system.
        OldAssets (List<Object>) List of assets being imported which already exist on the system.
        Parameters:
        importInfoNodePath - path of the node in repository which contains the asset import info
        Returns:
        list of assets being imported
        Throws:
        ICCException
        Since:
        6.2
